description: The acquisitions list of the Research Archives was formally published from 1991 to 1994. From February 2000 until February 2002, this list was distributed via email and archived online ( http://oi.uchicago.edu/OI/DEPT/RA/RABooks.html ). In recent years, the acquisitions list has only been distributed informally to Oriental Institute faculty, staff and students.
